SUMMARY:Ludum Dare 59
DESCRIPTION:Whether you’re a game jam veteran or have never made a video game before\, all are welcome to join us online and make a game in a weekend! Team up with other BIG members\, bring your own team\, or work solo. \nJoin us for the theme announcement\, then stay connected through the weekend to discuss game ideas\, find team members\, and coordinate on your jam entry. \nLudum Dare 59: https://ludumdare.com/ \n 
URL:https://baltimoreindiegames.com/event/ludum-dare-59/
LOCATION:MD
END:VEVENT
